<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Our Facilities</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Academic/facilities.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&family=Droid+Serif:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    <header class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Our Facilities & Infrastructure</h1>
            <p>A State-of-the-Art Environment for Learning and Growth</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            
            <section class="intro-section">
                <p>
                    Karuna Shanti is not just another Programme Project Campus; it stands out from the rest with its state-of-the-art infrastructure and cutting-edge technology support. Our spacious classrooms provide the perfect environment for fatigue-free teaching and learning, enhanced with modern technology to ensure an optimal educational experience.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="image-grid-section">
                <div class="image-grid">
                    <img src="/Academic/Images/4th.png" alt="Campus Building">
                    <img src="/Academic/Images/3rd.png" alt="Campus Classroom">
                    <img src="/Academic/Images/2nd.png" alt="Campus Hallway">
                    <img src="/Academic/Images/1st.png" alt="Campus Exterior">
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="checklist-section">
                <h3>What We Offer</h3>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <ul>
                        <li>School-like discipline with tuition-like teaching.</li>
                        <li>Orientation for entrance exams from day one.</li>
                        <li>Bridge courses and communicative English for all students.</li>
                        <li>Highly qualified, friendly, and dedicated faculty members.</li>
                        <li>Fully air-conditioned classrooms with modern amenities.</li>
                        <li>Personality development classes, yoga, and cultural programs.</li>
                        <li>A "Home Away From Home" hostel facility for boys and girls.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="facility-cards-section">
                <h3>Detailed Facilities</h3>
                <div class="facility-cards">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
                        <h4>LIBRARY</h4>
                        <p>Our library offers a vast collection of books, journals, and digital resources in a serene ambiance, providing the perfect space for students to focus and immerse themselves in their studies.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-home"></i></div>
                        <h4>HOSTEL</h4>
                        <p>We provide separate, well-maintained hostels for boys and girls with in-house superintendents, furnished rooms, and a hygienic mess to ensure a comfortable and homely environment.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-bus"></i></div>
                        <h4>TRANSPORT</h4>
                        <p>We offer safe, punctual, and cost-effective transportation services for our day-boarding students, making it easier for them to commute and focus on their studies without hassle.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-flask"></i></div>
                        <h4>LABORATORY</h4>
                        <p>Our state-of-the-art science laboratories are equipped with advanced instruments and staffed by experienced instructors to provide an immersive, hands-on learning experience.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i></div>
                        <h4>CDF & ZERO ERROR POLICY</h4>
                        <p>We reinforce foundational concepts through weekly tests and employ a zero-error policy with systematic rectification to ensure students achieve mastery and confidence in their subjects.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i></div>
                        <h4>KASH ONLINE REPLICA</h4>
                        <p>Our unique online platform allows students to take mock tests for NEET and JEE from anywhere, providing detailed personalized analysis to stay well-practiced for competitive exams.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>